{"tid":627971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平：將於海南設「自由貿易港」","createTime":"2018-04-13T11:59:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T02:23:06.000Z","uid":38671,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"6f2608bbe1dcd396e20fad8f080f94e2989a364d","tid":627971,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T11:59:56.000Z","msg":"上海自貿區呢？前海呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n據央廣網，習近平出席海南建省辦經濟特區30週年會議，強調支持海南推進改革開放。席間，習近平更公佈，計劃在海南建設自由貿易試驗區，於海南建設自由貿易港。他表示，支持海南設立國際能源、航運大宗商品等交易場所。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，海南建設自由貿易港消息早有傳聞，航基股份（357）更借消息率先炒上，自8.5元左右起步，最高炒至10.96元。今日收報10.3元，跌1.3%。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180413/58069669\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180413%2F58069669&d=Voc7XZDaq3ERB9ldoR2bIXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=d6d2d45d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180413%2F58069669&h=c5e74d30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180413/58069669</a>"},{"pid":"f530111153ab546a9784cdf8906068bd637a2ac8","tid":627971,"uid":51753,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T12:03:03.000Z","msg":"帶未開盒 iphone 新奇士橙 一箱hdd 過關可以唔洗俾人拉？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係先講自由啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d6a7461968863b616dd07abf4e91f62b0e16c59","tid":627971,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f530111153ab546a9784cdf8906068bd637a2ac8","tid":627971,"uid":51753,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T12:03:03.000Z","msg":"帶未開盒 iphone 新奇士橙 一箱hdd 過關可以唔洗俾人拉？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係先講自由啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T12:04:23.000Z","msg":"放低左比海關咪唔會比人拉囉<img src=\"/assets/fa